<body>
  <h1>Shared-State Concurrency Bug: Progress Bar Demo</h1>
  <p>Two panels: left shows a buggy shared-state update approach; right shows a corrected approach that avoids races. Both run the same simulated tasks concurrently.</p>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="panel" id="bug-panel">
      <div class="title-row">
        <h2 style="margin:0">Buggy: Shared Mutable Progress</h2>
