  <h1>Shared-State Progress Bug — Buggy vs Fixed</h1>
  <p class="small">This demo launches many concurrent asynchronous tasks that each claim some progress. The left panel shows a buggy approach that updates a shared numeric percent directly. The right panel shows a corrected approach that avoids the race by aggregating independent contributions or by using atomic update logic.</p>

  <div class="container">
