<body>
<h1>Progress Bar Concurrency Bug Demo</h1>
<p>Left: buggy implementation that updates a shared progress variable from multiple async tasks (race conditions possible). Right: corrected implementation that avoids races. Use "Start run" multiple times and "Start many tasks" to amplify races.</p>

<div class="container">
  <div class="card" id="buggyCard">
